    <h1 class="display-lg post-title">NEXA Mortgage Becomes NEXA Lending: What Changed and What It Means for Loan Officers and Homebuyers</h1>
    <div class="post-byline"><span class="mono">By Jim Blackburn · NMLS #1072866</span><span class="post-byline__sep">·</span><time datetime="2025-11-16">2025-11-16</time></div>
  </header>

