    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/NEXA-Mortgage-vs-NEXA-Lending-.png" alt="NEXA Mortgage Becomes NEXA Lending: What Changed and What It Means for Loan Officers and Homebuyers" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
